Marine data format
GRIB, HDF are used for gridded or raster data
netCDF can support station data and gridded data
BUFR is used operationally for real-time global exchange of weather and ocean observations on the GTS
These formats contain extensive internal metadata providing user systems with all the information needed for both data discovery and practical usage.
